  |  ------------------                    +-----------------+  |
  |  no.| chars cc. cp.                    |Set of characters|  |
  |  ------------------                    |to guess with:   |  |
  |    1|  [33mab[0m   [[32m0[0m] [[32m0[0m]                    +-----------------+  |
  |    2|  [33mcd[0m   [[32m1[0m] [[32m0[0m]                    |[33mabcdef[0m           |  |
  | [32mGuess:[0m _                               +-----------------+  |
  |                                                             |
  |                                                             |
  | For more options, type: [7m chadet --help [0m                     |
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
â—™ | At first, you have to blindly guess the characters.         |
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
â—™ | After each guess, computer will give you answer on how many |
  | characters you guessed correctly (Correct Characters or     |
  | cc.) and how many characters that their positions you       |
  | guessed correctly (Correct Positions or cp.).               |
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
â—™ | By analizing computer answers in the previous guesses, you  |
  | can guess inteligently what comes next.                     |
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+
â—™ | You can type [7m quit [0m or [7m hint [0m during the game. Their names  |
  | should imply what they can do.                              |
  +-------------------------------------------------------------+

